"n.不幸；不恰当 【考】 反义词：appropriate ness(适当) 【记】 in(不)+felic(得体)+ ity n. 不幸; 不合适 【反】appropriateness(n 适当) 【记】in 不 + felicity 恰当,幸福 infelicity (n.)  late 14c., from Latin infelicitas ""ill luck, misfortune,"" from infelix (genitive infelicis) ""unfruitful, barren; unfortunate, unhappy, causing misfortune, unlucky,"" from in- ""not, opposite of"" (see in- (1)) + felix (see felicity)."
